sarien (0.7.0-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Move sarien from contrib to main
    Sarien was orginally put in contrib because it needed the data files
    from the original Sierra games. With agistudio you can make you own
    games and sarien thus doesn't need anything not in Debian to be useable
    (except creativity maybe).
  * Bumped Standards-Version to 3.5.9

 -- Peter Makholm <peter@makholm.net>  Fri, 25 Apr 2003 18:35:19 +0200

